{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act23side", "eventName": "登臨意", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "WB-9", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "“冬藏”", "storyInfo": "重岳擊敗了睚，以自己的方式為玉門討了說法，隨後將劍託付給槐天裴，二人約定四十年後再比一場。玉門受損的城體需要兩個月才能修復，得到情報的睚再次上路。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_bat_act23side_02_intro", "key": "$m_bat_act23side_02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g12_huanjing", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g12_huanjing", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是第二次，在漫長的混沌中跋涉。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在跋涉的盡頭甦醒——"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "懊悔。屈辱。不甘。渾噩。"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更多的是，困惑。"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sphere"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g12_huanjing", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你要留我，那就替祂，回答我的問題！", "name": "睚"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monsteroar", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 35.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了見你，我一路走來。", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可知道，目之所見，那些愚妄的螻蟻，挖開岩脈，鑿穿河床，山嶽湖澤，清濁倒易，他們將那些猙獰的瘡疤，命名為城市......", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片早已病變的土地，還是我們曾棲居嬉遊的宇？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可知道，這座名為玉門的醜陋城市，磚牆上還留著當初祂們臨死前烙下的爪痕。", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "千年以來，那群螻蟻至今不曾修補那一塊地方，視之為榮耀，視之為文明的巍峨里程。", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而你的碎片，如今卻在守護這樣一座城？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是我，祂是祂。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sandstone"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 35.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（天地的隱怒）", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船仍在行進。"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩岸的草木矮去幾分，雪壓得更低了。"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可還記得，我們的意識如何跋涉於無寐的混沌，成為此間最初的生靈？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可還記得，我們如何注視著鴻蒙升落，時得其序，物分其列，天地慢慢有了天地的樣子？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可還記得，那破開雲靄的眼睛？我們在蒼穹間對視，碰撞，川江淤赤，群山夷為平地，伏屍聳入雲霄，潰膿腐爛後化作新的峰嶺......", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#6$2"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#4$2"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monsteroar", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 35.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是何等壯闊的，真正的，戰爭？！", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#4$2"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sandstone"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 35.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（天地的隱怒）", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船仍在行進，江面隨著船頭延伸，永無止境。"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "積雪更深，每一句發問，回聲都如同雪崩。"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上下皆白，天穹低得觸手可及。"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "經歷過那樣的時代，為何還會在意自己鱗爪間的螻蟻，和螻蟻撲騰起的塵埃？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了愚弄人類，你吹雲作雨，降下可笑的“祥瑞”，助所謂的真龍贏下征伐，本就無聊至極......", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又為何千年之後，再次回應他們？驚擾、挑唆、圍逐、驅殺自己的，同類？！", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相比他們渺小卻勇敢的先族，這幫羸弱的、不堪的、骯髒的螻蟻，你為何想要成為他們的主宰——？！", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "成為他們可笑的“神”？！", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sandstone"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（天地的隱怒）", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#4$2"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 35.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窮極寰宇，歷數太古以來無垠的時間，我們這樣的存在，可曾有過你這般恥辱？！", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#4$2"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回答我，我的......同類！"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 35.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_monsteroar", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很憤怒。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在沉睡的數千年裡，祂也無時無刻不像現在的你一樣......", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吞咽屈辱，咀嚼背叛，追問答案。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然也不會有我們這些碎片的誕生。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們已然不是祂。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#4$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你的問題，我給不了答案。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我理解不了你的憤怒，正如你理解不了我的憤怒。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憤怒？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#5$2"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#4$2"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你依然要為人類討要說法？在這裡？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#4$2"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拔出那把劍，或許還有可能。", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#4$2"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在想，你是有多麼珍惜這個空間。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g3_yumenobservationtower_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g5_swordcastingworkshop", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g2_yumenstreet_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g12_huanjing", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "春生夏榮秋傷冬藏，裁錯春秋，剪宇懷腹。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我甚至能想像到，你在千年前逃離炎國時，是怎樣將這幾方小小的天地剪裁下來倉皇帶走。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而後又是怎樣隱匿在這片大地上某個僻遠的角落，一遍又一遍地翻檢查看，就著永遠不會流逝的殘景舔舐傷口。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨獸，也變成了如此傷懷的一種生命？！", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這和你口中那般羸弱的、不堪的、骯髒的人類，又有什麼區別？！", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "delay": 0.2, "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "八千年為春，八千年為秋，雪永遠不會停，這方天地永遠是這天地。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是你們丈量時間的方式......", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是可笑。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#3$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "日、月、年。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寒來暑往，一載春秋。"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論多麼漫長的時間，也可以拆成一寸寸光陰。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一心一意，一招一式，從三九到三伏，再到下一個三九。"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人類從來都是如此，將生命拆解成微末，再從微末中感受一切。"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#8$1", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_punchsp2"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$glass"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g12_huanjing", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 5.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "船停了——"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結結實實的拳頭，轟在睚的胸膛上。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有多餘的動作，萬法歸一，武道至簡。"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "漫天冰雪融作江心一點，睚的身體跌出小舟......"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "重重砸在冷硬的地面上。"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g7_zuosroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$storyendjp_intro", "key": "$storyendjp_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就是......你放棄祂的力量後習得的本事......", "name": "睚"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的確不是祂......", "name": "睚"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#3$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人沒有說話，他沉默地看著眼前奄奄一息的“人”。"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來萬千生靈，在瀕死之時都是相似的姿態。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼......不殺了我？", "name": "睚"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "代理人的身軀，你可以隨意捏塑，毀掉了也沒有意義。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開玉門。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "睚"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還會再見的。", "name": "睚"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_humanchange"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳......", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#2$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g3_yumenobservationtower_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowstormflp", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$newhope01_intro", "key": "$newhope01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_armour"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "將軍，受災情況初步清點完畢。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人員傷亡如何？", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天災到來前，城東的百姓已經安全遷往城西。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欽天監術師在核心內城正面對抗二次風暴，有近半數受傷。當時龍門的林先生林特使父女也在場相助......林先生受傷很重。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#2$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已、已經送往軍營醫館。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林先生仗義出手，於玉門有大恩，全力救治，不容有失。", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#7$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "建築受損情況。", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城西並未受到影響，南北兩區在天災最為嚴重時受風沙侵襲，部分建築有不同程度的損壞......", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城東直面沙塵與源石塵暴，情況最為嚴重。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玉門四衛中兩組破損嚴重，失去了修補價值，土木天師已將其直接脫離。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "關鍵是基礎牆體也受到了影響，部分立面結構嚴重錯位，需要進行緊急加固。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他城防工事的折耗率在六成左右。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#8$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "土木天師是否有了結論？", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#8$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據幾位天師初步計算，以最快的速度修復牆體工事，至少需要兩個月的時間，玉門城才能重新恢復航行。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個月......", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#2$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情況竟比災前預估的要好上一些。", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傳令。", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尚不清楚天災是否有餘波，全體軍士不可懈怠。", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續清點災情，送傷者就醫，增設臨時營帳，將百姓從城西避難點遷出妥善安置。", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城中的山海眾？", "name": "左宣遼"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "山海眾試圖襲擊沙渠等城防工事、侵擾百姓來製造混亂，巡防營應對及時，加上武行的人出手相助，多數都已伏法。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只有少數人趁著牆體破壞逃出了城。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嗯。", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#8$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但此前潛入軍營行刺的山海眾首領並沒有現身，已經增派人手進行搜捕。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有現身？", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#10$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以那人的本事，竟沒有趁亂做些什麼......", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#10$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宗師呢？", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#1$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "宗師去了一趟鑄劍坊後，人也不見了。", "name": "巡防營守軍"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_796_1#1$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_788_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "左宣遼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_788_1#8$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g9_yumensuburb", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你把這把劍塞給我，是什麼意思？", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望閣下代為保管......算是一個請求。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來就是為了這把劍，鬧得滿城風雨。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#6$1"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這到底是什麼東西？", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#1$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它的確有太多的身份。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "封印了歲獸十二分之一意識的器物，一段愛恨糾葛的見證，一把有些年頭的古劍。"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可以把它當作他日我們再戰的信物。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要別再讓它被人偷去搶去，或是把它典當換錢就好。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這應該是件挺重要的物件。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是閣下覺得為難的話......", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#6$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是在想......或許我們不算認識。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#11$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你叫槐天裴，有兩位聰明的朋友，和一個伶俐的女兒。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#10$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還知道你是從古至今，唯一一個贏了我一拳的人。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#10$1"}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#9$1"}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你是我習武四十年，唯一打不過的那個。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#9$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scabbard"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_785_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這把劍，我帶著。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#9$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等我再練四十年，再來找你。", "name": "槐天裴"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_785_1#9$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_2024_chyue_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#10$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我等閣下。", "name": "重岳"}, "figure_art": "avg_2024_chyue_1#10$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g13_yanlivingroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫生，我想向您打聽一下。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前留在您醫館的那位夥計，他還欠您多少藥錢，我替他還給您。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算啦。都這麼久了，哪還欠我什麼錢。", "name": "醫生"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無非是找個理由，讓他有個安身的地方。", "name": "醫生"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幫忙做些救死扶傷的事，總好過整天打打殺殺的......", "name": "醫生"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常，謝謝您......", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#7$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是他女兒？", "name": "醫生"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個人瘋瘋癲癲，居然有這麼一位知書達理的女兒，真是奇怪。", "name": "醫生"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#5$1"}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過少了這麼一位夥計，還真有點不習慣。", "name": "醫生"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看這一屋子落沙，我自己怎麼收拾得過來喲......", "name": "醫生"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我、我來幫您！", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是不告而別？", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#4$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 369, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底還是他......", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#8$1"}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過這次，我也不再急著去把他找出來了。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來，接下來你也做好了打算。", "name": "老鯉"}, "figure_art": "avg_322_lmlee_1#10$1"}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "偵探事務所那邊的工作我會繼續做，學業也會繼續。當然，武功更不會擱下。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下次再見他的時候，就不只是踢他下巴了。", "name": "槐琥"}, "figure_art": "avg_243_waaifu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "StopMusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_g11_yumendesert", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper1"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "上面來信，我們稍事整頓，趕赴下一個任務地點。", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惜玉門城還是安然渡過了天災，而我們傷亡慘重。", "name": "著急的山海眾成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（冷哼聲）", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_woodcracle"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信函在蒙面男人的手中燃燒，紙張很快化為灰燼，但一小方金色浴火後反而更加奪目。"}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是特製的火漆，專供朝中一品要員，三公重卿，能使用者不超過五人。"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "男人將火漆攥在手裡，把玩片刻後輕輕捏碎。細屑散入沙塵，消失不見。"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來的任務，也只是製造一場足夠引起朝廷注意的動靜，玉門城還有大用，要真毀了，反倒得不償失。", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "著急的山海眾成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即刻撤離。", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不等先生嗎？這次沒她幫忙，我們很難成事。", "name": "著急的山海眾成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_800_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是諦獸......先生回來了！", "name": "著急的山海眾成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_794_1#1$1"}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心......", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "玉門城裡，有誰能讓先生受這麼重的傷？！", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 424, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個“人”。", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打聽到別的消息沒有？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_800_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（詭異的長鳴）", "name": "諦獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多長時間？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_800_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（詭異的長鳴）", "name": "諦獸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_800_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩個月？", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......足夠了。", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#2$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經知道了祂的位置。", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 28.0, "ystrength": 26.0, "vibrato": 40.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的目的......您究竟是......", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，我們恐怕要就此別過。", "name": "山海眾頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨你們......", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別阻礙我做事。", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_793_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.2}}, {"id": 452, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "睚"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 456, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再漫長的路也有終點。"}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "被喚醒後，我愈發清晰地感受到它的到來——所謂“大限”。"}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那場圍獵中所受的傷，已不可能痊癒。"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你最好也已經醒了。"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我所剩無幾的時間，我所剩無幾的同類。"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們要，做個了結。"}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}